  "detailed_description": "<h1>PARTY ANIMALS DELUXE EDITION</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260320/extras/862c85960bfdf3f06f16ad90948953a9.avif?t=1770880496\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>Deluxe Edition includes:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Party Animals Base Game<br></li><li>Nemo Bucks*1300<br></li><li>Bathrobe Harry Outfit & Avatar & Frame<br></li><li>Bathrobe Coco Outfit & Avatar & Frame<br></li><li>Bathrobe Garfat Outfit & Avatar & Frame<br></li><li>Golden Nemo Skin & Avatar<br></li><li>Golden Macchiato Skin & Avatar<br></li><li>Golden Coco Skin & Avatar</li></ul></p><br><h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Make Painfully Great Memories with Your Friends in Party Animals. </h2><br><br><strong> Mess With Your Friend in 100 Different Ways</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260320/extras/ea12341010fbbd13bf0b82e0a7040c32.poster.avif?t=1770880496\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260320/extras/ea12341010fbbd13bf0b82e0a7040c32.webm?t=1770880496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260320/extras/ea12341010fbbd13bf0b82e0a7040c32.mp4?t=1770880496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Or Together You Could Eliminate Others</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260320/extras/95cf7e1dc2d7f4d911d6c9e9060f5970.poster.avif?t=1770880496\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260320/extras/95cf7e1dc2d7f4d911d6c9e9060f5970.webm?t=